        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/Paris/_scene_paris.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 335ce4e7-36bb-45cd-aa24-18564d48ed4e).Image",
        "Description": "Sheikh Al-Ghazali is in Paris to attend IAGO&apos;s auction, and it looks like he doesn&apos;t plan on leaving empty-handed. Three of his men have infiltrated the CICADA security team and are ready to step in should the auction not go his way. IAGO have caught wind of this but do not want to intervene themselves out of fear of upsetting the powerful Al-Ghazali family, and so they have reached out to the ICA to do it instead. Your task is to eliminate Al-Ghazali and the three CICADA moles.\rGood Luck 47.",
